{
	"nodes":[
		{
			"id":"8r8u8l9k",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# 4 光的传播",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"8:1372166193:180","lastWidth":180,"lastAutoHeight":102,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":102,"trustedSignature":"8:1372166193:180","trustedTimestamp":1772460809645},
				"fromLinkRepair":{"unmatched":true,"updatedAt":1772526754016}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"8:1372166193:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":60,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":60,"trustedSignature":"8:1372166193:200","trustedTimestamp":1772528714606},
			"x":0,
			"y":5370.014229024943,
			"width":200,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"z4pkbd0w",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## 4.1 简介",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"9:1901458132:180","lastWidth":180,"lastAutoHeight":56,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":56,"trustedSignature":"9:1901458132:180","trustedTimestamp":1772470732482},
				"fromLinkRepair":{"unmatched":true,"updatedAt":1772526754016}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"9:1901458132:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"9:1901458132:200","trustedTimestamp":1772527364485},
			"x":400,
			"y":778,
			"width":200,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"thy93dds",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 1. 三大宏观现象 (Macroscopic Phenomena)\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":15,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":15,\"ch\":39}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"37:2701785545:340","lastWidth":340,"lastAutoHeight":121,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":121,"trustedSignature":"37:2701785545:340","trustedTimestamp":1772460809645}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"145:3027855730:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":96,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":96,"trustedSignature":"145:3027855730:400","trustedTimestamp":1772526777403},
			"x":1000,
			"y":1341,
			"width":400,
			"height":96
		},
		{
			"id":"5ejxtw2q",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**透射 (Transmission):** 光穿过介质继续传播的现象。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":17,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":17,\"ch\":42}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"36:2758569472:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":64,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":64,"trustedSignature":"36:2758569472:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809645}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"144:3708665793:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"144:3708665793:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527364485},
			"x":1600,
			"y":1226,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"ghb3ywve",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**反射 (Reflection):** 光在两种介质界面上改变传播方向返回原介质的现象。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":18,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":18,\"ch\":51}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"45:1008773201:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":64,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":64,"trustedSignature":"45:1008773201:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809646}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"153:1723387826:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"153:1723387826:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527587207},
			"x":1600,
			"y":1345,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"vzmrxead",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**折射 (Refraction):** 光从一种介质进入另一种介质时，由于速度改变而导致传播方向发生偏折的现象。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":19,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":19,\"ch\":63}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"57:1095116035:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":88,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":88,"trustedSignature":"57:1095116035:400","trustedTimestamp":1772470732530}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"165:3149856327:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":103,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":103,"trustedSignature":"165:3149856327:400","trustedTimestamp":1772526782705},
			"x":1600,
			"y":1464,
			"width":400,
			"height":103
		},
		{
			"id":"pdyl5z2o",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 2. 三大理论描述工具 (Theoretical Frameworks)\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":21,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":21,\"ch\":42}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"40:256004360:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":88,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":88,"trustedSignature":"40:256004360:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809647}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"148:459898111:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":96,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":96,"trustedSignature":"148:459898111:400","trustedTimestamp":1772526760656},
			"x":1000,
			"y":147,
			"width":400,
			"height":96
		},
		{
			"id":"5jahc01n",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**几何光学与波动光学 (Rays and Waves):** 最基础的描述方式。将光简化为沿直线传播的“光线”或具有周期性的“波动”。这足以处理大部分工程问题（如透镜成像），但无法解释光与物质相互作用的本质。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":23,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":23,\"ch\":109}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"105:929933528:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":112,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":112,"trustedSignature":"105:929933528:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460799305}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"214:3695578563:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"214:3695578563:400","trustedTimestamp":1772526762473},
			"x":1600,
			"y":-40,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"88r6u9et",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**电磁理论 (Electromagnetic Theory):** 在经典物理框架下，将光视为交变的电磁场。通过麦克斯韦方程组描述电磁波在介质中的传播，能更严谨地推导出反射和折射定律。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":24,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":24,\"ch\":97}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"93:848162319:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":112,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":112,"trustedSignature":"93:848162319:400","trustedTimestamp":1772470732553}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"201:306569322:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"201:306569322:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527364486},
			"x":1600,
			"y":127,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"938rc5ls",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**量子电动力学 (Quantum Electrodynamics, QED):** 最现代、最本质的理论。它将光视为**光子 (Photons)**，将物质视为原子阵列，通过量子力学描述光子与带电粒子（主要是电子）之间的相互作用。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":25,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":25,\"ch\":120}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"116:2355393174:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":160,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":160,"trustedSignature":"116:2355393174:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809648}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"225:3010319030:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":151,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":151,"trustedSignature":"225:3010319030:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527364486},
			"x":1600,
			"y":294,
			"width":400,
			"height":151
		},
		{
			"id":"p3f1y59j",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 3. 核心微观机制：散射 (Scattering)\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":27,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":27,\"ch\":31}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"29:1137388741:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":88,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":88,"trustedSignature":"29:1137388741:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809648}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"137:879225384:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":96,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":96,"trustedSignature":"137:879225384:400","trustedTimestamp":1772526775313},
			"x":1000,
			"y":785,
			"width":400,
			"height":96
		},
		{
			"id":"dacyk951",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"所有的宏观光学现象本质上都是**散射**的结果\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":28,\"ch\":51},\"to\":{\"line\":28,\"ch\":74}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"23:3926653768:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":40,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":40,"trustedSignature":"23:3926653768:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809648}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"132:2600049472:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"132:2600049472:400","trustedTimestamp":1772526774129},
			"x":1600,
			"y":485,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"p92shis2",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**散射的定义:** 在微观层面，光（电磁辐射）被原子或分子中的电子**吸收 (Absorption)** 并随后**立即重新发射 (Prompt Re-emission)** 的过程。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":29,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":29,\"ch\":97}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"93:3553495597:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":124,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":124,"trustedSignature":"93:3553495597:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809648}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"201:933805842:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":103,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":103,"trustedSignature":"201:933805842:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527364486},
			"x":1600,
			"y":580,
			"width":400,
			"height":103
		},
		{
			"id":"ogwpgpe2",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**协同行为 (Cooperative Behavior):** 宏观上的反射或透射，并不是单一原子的行为，而是无数原子在电磁场作用下产生的协同效应。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":30,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":30,\"ch\":79}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"75:1658770894:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":88,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":88,"trustedSignature":"75:1658770894:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809648}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"183:3267908387:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":103,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":103,"trustedSignature":"183:3267908387:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527364486},
			"x":1600,
			"y":723,
			"width":400,
			"height":103
		},
		{
			"id":"nwgcege4",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"$$ \\text{微观：光子} + \\text{原子/电子} \\xrightarrow{\\text{相互作用}} \\text{散射 (吸收与再发射)} $$\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":37,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":37,\"ch\":80}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"manualHeight":false,"lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":82,"lastSignature":"78:225332500:400","trustedHeight":82,"trustedSignature":"78:225332500:400","trustedTimestamp":1772470742495}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"trustedHeight":64,"trustedSignature":"186:3268447183:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527532856,"lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":64},
			"x":1600,
			"y":866,
			"width":400,
			"height":80
		},
		{
			"id":"o4aimwe1",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"$$ \\downarrow (\\text{大量粒子的协同效应}) $$\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":38,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":38,\"ch\":37}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"manualHeight":false,"lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":80,"lastSignature":"35:2096028818:400","trustedHeight":80,"trustedSignature":"35:2096028818:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809648}
			},
			"x":1600,
			"y":986,
			"width":400,
			"height":80
		},
		{
			"id":"f4e0ym39",
			"type":"text",
			"text":" $$ \\text{宏观表现：透射、反射、折射} $$\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":39,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":39,\"ch\":28}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"manualHeight":false,"lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":80,"lastSignature":"27:1048291514:400","trustedHeight":80,"trustedSignature":"27:1048291514:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809649}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"trustedHeight":50,"trustedSignature":"135:817555015:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527588239,"lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":50},
			"x":1600,
			"y":1106,
			"width":400,
			"height":80
		},
		{
			"id":"bulfkoqh",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## 4.2 瑞利散射 \n(Rayleigh Scattering)\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":228,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":228,\"ch\":33}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"34:1247073014:260","lastWidth":260,"lastAutoHeight":96,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":96,"trustedSignature":"34:1247073014:260","trustedTimestamp":1772460809649}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"144:451818075:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":111,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":111,"trustedSignature":"144:451818075:400","trustedTimestamp":1772539519377},
			"x":400,
			"y":4523,
			"width":400,
			"height":111
		},
		{
			"id":"636vernw",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**光子是永恒的 (Photons are timeless)**：\n<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">在真空中，一个 光子 ( Photon) 一旦被创造出来，除非它与物质发生相互作用，否则它将永远以光速 $c$ 运动下去，其能量和频率都不会改变。</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":233,\"ch\":104},\"to\":{\"line\":233,\"ch\":248}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"152:648357962:420","lastWidth":420,"lastAutoHeight":112,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":112,"trustedSignature":"152:648357962:420","trustedTimestamp":1772470734675}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"265:1465105566:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":120,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"265:1684061956:400","trustedTimestamp":1772526785139},
			"x":1000,
			"y":1607,
			"width":400,
			"height":120
		},
		{
			"id":"pskw3aow",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"<mark style=\"background: #FF5582A6;\">弹性散射 ( Elastic-Scattering)</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":239,\"ch\":134},\"to\":{\"line\":239,\"ch\":160}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"70:775666818:340","lastWidth":340,"lastAutoHeight":52,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":52,"trustedSignature":"70:775666818:340","trustedTimestamp":1772006930403}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"183:2213796638:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"183:2213796638:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527587207},
			"x":1000,
			"y":2066,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"b4w9511p",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"我们往这片虚空中混入一缕空气——也就是一些氮气、氧气等气体分子。<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">这些分子在可见光波段没有 共振 ( Resonance) 频率</mark>。这意味着，它们无法通过吸收一个可见光光子，就从基态跃迁到一个能量更高的激发态。因此，对于可见光而言，这些气体是透明的。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":235,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":235,\"ch\":171}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"167:208267657:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":265,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":265,"trustedSignature":"167:208267657:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006895918}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"278:2523608181:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":136,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":175,"trustedSignature":"278:2716607481:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527587207},
			"x":1600,
			"y":1767,
			"width":400,
			"height":136
		},
		{
			"id":"jucvx1d7",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 4.2.1 散射强度与频率的关系：天空为何是蓝色的？\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":249,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":249,\"ch\":30}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"30:1046398544:340","lastWidth":340,"lastAutoHeight":78,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":78,"trustedSignature":"30:1046398544:340","trustedTimestamp":1772006930403}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"140:646398802:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":96,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":96,"trustedSignature":"140:646398802:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527356100},
			"x":1000,
			"y":3071,
			"width":400,
			"height":96
		},
		{
			"id":"g4674zum",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"这些气体分子与光是如何相互作用的呢？它们表现得像一个个微小的振子。当入射光（电磁波）到来时，其交变的电场会驱动分子中的电子云，使其围绕原子核进行受迫振动。这种振动并非电子能级的跃迁，而是一种在基态附近的振动。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":237,\"ch\":3},\"to\":{\"line\":237,\"ch\":107}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"104:3623463336:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":229,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":229,"trustedSignature":"104:3623463336:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006895918}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"215:2807954820:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":151,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":151,"trustedSignature":"215:2807954820:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527587207},
			"x":1600,
			"y":1943,
			"width":400,
			"height":151
		},
		{
			"id":"mh48gp2m",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"这个振动的电子云本身就构成了一个振荡的电偶极子，它会立即向外辐射电磁波——也就是重新发射出光。这个过程是：一个光子被吸收，紧接着，另一个频率（和波长）完全相同的光子被发射出来。我们称这种过程为 <mark style=\"background: #FF5582A6;\">弹性散射 ( Elastic-Scattering)</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":239,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":239,\"ch\":160}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"167:1406578087:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":136,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":136,"trustedSignature":"167:1406578087:400","trustedTimestamp":1772470744094}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"278:914129787:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":116,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":151,"trustedSignature":"278:2532572965:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527590541},
			"x":1600,
			"y":2134,
			"width":400,
			"height":116
		},
		{
			"id":"27orskl0",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"由于气体分子是随机取向的，这些被重新发射的光子会朝向四面八方散射出去\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":239,\"ch\":168},\"to\":{\"line\":239,\"ch\":202}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"34:3899857154:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":87,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":87,"trustedSignature":"34:3899857154:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006930403}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"147:1268397734:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"147:1268397734:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527590541},
			"x":1600,
			"y":2290,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"04tm5qk9",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"这与我们前面提到的“振子模型”和“共振”概念密切相关。虽然空气分子在可见光区没有共振，但它们在能量更高的紫外（UV）区有电子共振频率。根据受迫振动的原理，驱动频率越接近一个系统的固有（共振）频率，振子的响应就越剧烈，振幅也越大。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":253,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":253,\"ch\":114}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"114:3805663619:345","lastWidth":345,"lastAutoHeight":197,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":197,"trustedSignature":"114:3805663619:345","trustedTimestamp":1772470742310}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"225:1089468872:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":175,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":175,"trustedSignature":"225:1089468872:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527356103},
			"x":1600,
			"y":2409,
			"width":400,
			"height":175
		},
		{
			"id":"qyv3h3fe",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"当蓝光或紫光照射到空气分子上时，会比红光更能激发电子云产生剧烈的振动\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":257,\"ch\":102},\"to\":{\"line\":257,\"ch\":136}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"34:3518034503:345","lastWidth":345,"lastAutoHeight":123,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":123,"trustedSignature":"34:3518034503:345","trustedTimestamp":1772006930403}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"147:3042561761:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"147:3042561761:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527356103},
			"x":1600,
			"y":2624,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"fu51sl53",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">一个振动得越剧烈的电荷，它向外辐射的电磁波（也就是散射光）的强度就越大</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":259,\"ch\":38},\"to\":{\"line\":259,\"ch\":73}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"79:3993309609:345","lastWidth":345,"lastAutoHeight":123,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":123,"trustedSignature":"79:3993309609:345","trustedTimestamp":1772006930403}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"190:3676138143:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"190:3676138143:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527356103},
			"x":1600,
			"y":2743,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"acngudk7",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"散射光强度 $I$ 与波长 $\\lambda$ 的四次方成反比的结论，也就是与频率 $\\nu$ 的四次方成正比：\n> $$\n> I \\propto \\nu^4 \\propto \\frac{1}{\\lambda^4}\n> $$\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":259,\"ch\":138},\"to\":{\"line\":259,\"ch\":194}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"112:1256198180:345","lastWidth":345,"lastAutoHeight":239,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":239,"trustedSignature":"112:1256198180:345","trustedTimestamp":1772006930403}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"225:901458585:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":194,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":194,"trustedSignature":"225:901458585:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527356103},
			"x":1600,
			"y":2862,
			"width":400,
			"height":194
		},
		{
			"id":"mqjnlrn3",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"<mark style=\"background: #FF5582A6;\">瑞利散射</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":264,\"ch\":7},\"to\":{\"line\":264,\"ch\":11}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"48:88380154:150","lastWidth":150,"lastAutoHeight":52,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":52,"trustedSignature":"48:88380154:150","trustedTimestamp":1772006930403}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"158:841381414:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"158:841381414:200","trustedTimestamp":1772526923094},
			"x":1600,
			"y":3108,
			"width":200,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"3n83x1s4",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"尺寸远小于波长的粒子（通常指小于 $\\lambda/10$）的散射\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":264,\"ch\":128},\"to\":{\"line\":264,\"ch\":168}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"33:3957489961:350","lastWidth":350,"lastAutoHeight":87,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":87,"trustedSignature":"33:3957489961:350","trustedTimestamp":1772006930403}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"146:3476369178:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"146:3476369178:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529246847},
			"x":2200,
			"y":3096,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"riw57jgf",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**应用到天空颜色：**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":280,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":280,\"ch\":12}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"12:388406039:210","lastWidth":210,"lastAutoHeight":52,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":52,"trustedSignature":"12:388406039:210","trustedTimestamp":1772006930403}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"122:3258329085:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"122:3258329085:200","trustedTimestamp":1772526808003},
			"x":1600,
			"y":3604,
			"width":200,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"6oikm4um",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**蓝天：** 蓝光的波长（约475 nm）比红光的波长（约650 nm）短。根据公式，蓝光被散射的强度大约是红光的 $(650/475)^4 \\approx (1.37)^4 \\approx 3.5$ 倍。紫光（约400 nm）的散射更强，大约是红光的 $(650/400)^4 \\approx (1.625)^4 \\approx 7$ 倍！当你看向天空时，你看到的是从各个方向散射到你眼睛里的太阳光。由于短波长的光被散射得更强烈，所以天空呈现出蓝色。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":281,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":281,\"ch\":229}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"227:4143944203:350","lastWidth":350,"lastAutoHeight":234,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":234,"trustedSignature":"227:4143944203:350","trustedTimestamp":1772460820091}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"338:2721180739:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":225,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":225,"trustedSignature":"338:2721180739:400","trustedTimestamp":1772526812503},
			"x":2200,
			"y":3215,
			"width":400,
			"height":225
		},
		{
			"id":"nf1of0sa",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**为什么不是紫色？** 尽管紫光散射最强，但天空看起来是淡蓝色，原因有三：\n>     1.  太阳光谱本身在蓝光部分的能量就比紫光部分要多。\n>     2.  人眼对蓝光的敏感度高于紫光。\n>     3.  大气散射的宽广频率范围（富含紫、蓝、绿光）被人眼平均后，感知为白色背景上叠加了一层鲜艳的蓝色（约476 nm），最终形成我们熟悉的淡蓝色天空。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":282,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":282,\"ch\":40}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"179:3561027953:350","lastWidth":350,"lastAutoHeight":466,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":466,"trustedSignature":"179:3561027953:350","trustedTimestamp":1772006930403}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"289:3335710516:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":311,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":311,"trustedSignature":"289:3335710516:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529246847},
			"x":2200,
			"y":3480,
			"width":400,
			"height":311
		},
		{
			"id":"7y5wi371",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**红色的日落：** 当太阳位于地平线附近时（日出或日落），阳光需要穿过非常厚的大气层才能到达你的眼睛。在这个漫长的路程中，大部分的蓝光和紫光都已经被散射到其他方向了，而散射较弱的红光和黄光则能“幸存”下来，沿着直线路径传播到你的眼中，因此太阳和周围的天空看起来是炽热的红色或橙色。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":286,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":286,\"ch\":143}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"141:3503849100:350","lastWidth":350,"lastAutoHeight":336,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":336,"trustedSignature":"141:3503849100:350","trustedTimestamp":1772007000804}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"252:1831292217:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":199,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":199,"trustedSignature":"252:1831292217:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527595619},
			"x":2200,
			"y":3831,
			"width":400,
			"height":199
		},
		{
			"id":"bykd2o35",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"因此，光谱中的蓝色端总是被散射得最多\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":288,\"ch\":137},\"to\":{\"line\":288,\"ch\":155}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"124:2358223914:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"124:2358223914:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007000804}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"131:856597015:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"131:856597015:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527595619},
			"x":2200,
			"y":4070,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"g4lhcmr4",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"人的蓝眼睛、蓝鸟的羽毛、蓝尾石龙子的蓝色尾巴以及狒狒的蓝色臀部，其颜色都源于瑞利散射。事实上，<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">在动物王国中，几乎所有的蓝色、大部分绿色，甚至一些紫色都是由散射引起的</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":288,\"ch\":156},\"to\":{\"line\":288,\"ch\":275}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"232:2276368202:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":216,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":216,"trustedSignature":"232:2276368202:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007000804}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"239:104359959:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"239:104359959:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529246848},
			"x":2200,
			"y":4165,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"q7ps5ubb",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 4.2.2 散射与干涉：从稀薄到致密\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":290,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":290,\"ch\":22}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"125:1511944515:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":59,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":59,"trustedSignature":"125:1511944515:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006755351}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"132:3400206156:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":97,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":97,"trustedSignature":"132:3400206156:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527610416},
			"x":1000,
			"y":4739,
			"width":400,
			"height":97
		},
		{
			"id":"mlkt799k",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 4.2.2.1 稀薄介质中的散射：无序与非相干\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":295,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":295,\"ch\":28}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"131:349366167:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":62,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":62,"trustedSignature":"131:349366167:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007009688}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"138:3105527684:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":91,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":91,"trustedSignature":"138:3105527684:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527610416},
			"x":1600,
			"y":4452,
			"width":400,
			"height":91
		},
		{
			"id":"9ynqo0gk",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**相位：** 波的 相位 ( Phase) 描述了它在周期中的位置（例如，是波峰还是波谷）。路径长度不同，意味着到达 $P$ 点的各个子波的相位是完全随机的、杂乱无章的（图 4.3b）。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":300,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":300,\"ch\":96}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"197:2765166420:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":216,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":216,"trustedSignature":"197:2765166420:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007000804}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"204:2032335289:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"204:2032335289:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527595619},
			"x":2200,
			"y":4332,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"23rmbme2",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**干涉效果：** 在 $P$ 点，这些来自不同分子的子波叠加在一起。由于相位随机，在任何时刻，都有些子波是波峰与波峰相遇（ 相长干涉 ( Constructive-Interference)），有些是波峰与波谷相遇（ 相消干涉 ( Destructive-Interference)）。这种混乱的、不断变化的叠加效果，使得总体的干涉效应被平均掉了。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":301,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":301,\"ch\":177}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"279:648767614:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":322,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":322,"trustedSignature":"279:648767614:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006755351}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"286:1887993193:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":199,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":199,"trustedSignature":"286:1887993193:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527610416},
			"x":2200,
			"y":4499,
			"width":400,
			"height":199
		},
		{
			"id":"ha027rhy",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 4.2.2.2 致密介质中的散射：有序与相干\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":307,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":307,\"ch\":27}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"130:3114185856:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":56,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":56,"trustedSignature":"130:3114185856:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006755351}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"137:1563251673:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":91,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":91,"trustedSignature":"137:1563251673:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527610416},
			"x":1600,
			"y":4792,
			"width":400,
			"height":91
		},
		{
			"id":"n15zy673",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**侧向相消干涉：** 如图 4.6 所示，想象光束穿过一个有序排列的散射体阵列。对于侧向的任何方向，由于原子排列紧密，我们几乎总能找到一个原子 $A$ 和另一个原子 $B$，它们到远处观察点的光程差恰好是半个波长 ($\\lambda/2$) 的奇数倍。这意味着，从 $A$ 和 $B$ 发出的子波在那个方向上会发生相消干涉（波峰与波谷叠加），从而相互抵消。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":311,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":311,\"ch\":181}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"283:494299830:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":321,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":321,"trustedSignature":"283:494299830:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006755351}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"290:1129320259:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":199,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":199,"trustedSignature":"290:1129320259:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527610416},
			"x":2200,
			"y":4738,
			"width":400,
			"height":199
		},
		{
			"id":"6bqlai04",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 4.2.2.3 前向传播的奥秘\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":323,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":323,\"ch\":20}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"123:4183130561:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":56,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":56,"trustedSignature":"123:4183130561:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006755351}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"130:2434589322:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":90,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":90,"trustedSignature":"130:2434589322:200","trustedTimestamp":1772527610417},
			"x":1600,
			"y":4984,
			"width":200,
			"height":90
		},
		{
			"id":"4mghjlly",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"既然侧向散射被抑制了，那能量去哪儿了？答案是：它们都在前向发生了相长干涉，使得光束得以继续前进。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":324,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":324,\"ch\":48}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"151:3639235892:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"151:3639235892:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006755351}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"158:1853121603:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":104,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":104,"trustedSignature":"158:1853121603:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527610417},
			"x":2200,
			"y":4977,
			"width":400,
			"height":104
		},
		{
			"id":"iizonw3j",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 4.2.3 从散射到折射率：光的传播速度之谜\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":338,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":338,\"ch\":26}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"129:2962030990:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":88,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":88,"trustedSignature":"129:2962030990:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007009692}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"136:3890302185:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":97,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":97,"trustedSignature":"136:3890302185:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527637631},
			"x":1000,
			"y":5681,
			"width":400,
			"height":97
		},
		{
			"id":"3a6ocg0p",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">光在介质中的“变慢”并不是单个光子飞得慢了，而是整个波的 **相位传播** 变慢了。这是由散射和再发射过程中的 **相位延迟** 造成的。</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":341,\"ch\":62},\"to\":{\"line\":341,\"ch\":131}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"218:2056954114:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":180,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":180,"trustedSignature":"218:2056954114:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006755351}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"225:3117038667:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":103,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":103,"trustedSignature":"225:1209149547:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527637631},
			"x":1600,
			"y":5121,
			"width":400,
			"height":103
		},
		{
			"id":"thk6e6rb",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**振子的相位滞后：** 让我们再次回到受迫振动的模型。一个被驱动的振子，其振动相位通常会滞后于驱动力的相位。滞后的程度取决于驱动频率与共振频率的相对关系（如图 4.9b 所示）。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":343,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":343,\"ch\":94}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"193:608180120:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":216,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":216,"trustedSignature":"193:608180120:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006755351}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"200:2513059253:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"200:2513059253:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527637631},
			"x":1600,
			"y":5288,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"34xos1ap",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"    *   在远低于共振频率时（例如可见光对于玻璃），相位滞后接近90度。\n    *   当频率接近共振时，相位滞后接近90度。\n    *   在共振频率处，相位滞后为90度。\n    *   在远高于共振频率时，相位滞后接近180度。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":344,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":344,\"ch\":39}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"225:507640433:640","lastWidth":640,"lastAutoHeight":176,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":176,"trustedSignature":"225:507640433:640","trustedTimestamp":1772006755351}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"232:2341033294:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":175,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":175,"trustedSignature":"232:825911090:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527637631},
			"x":2200,
			"y":5264,
			"width":400,
			"height":175
		},
		{
			"id":"8ofi7k97",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**次级波的相位：** 所有的振子（分子）都在振动，它们共同产生的次级波，其相位又会相对于振子们的振动相位滞后90度（这是一个电动力学的结果，我们可以暂时接受这个结论）。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":349,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":349,\"ch\":89}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"188:2001314890:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":216,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":216,"trustedSignature":"188:2001314890:400","trustedTimestamp":1772006755351}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"195:2763634639:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"195:2763634639:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527637631},
			"x":1600,
			"y":5479,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"mqbselh5",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**波的叠加与表观速度：** 在介质中，我们观测到的透射波是原初波和次级波的叠加。如图 4.11 所示，当一个相位滞后的次级波与原初波叠加时，得到的合波（透射波）的相位也会相对于原初波发生滞后。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":353,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":353,\"ch\":101}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"201:3376825653:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":216,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":216,"trustedSignature":"201:3376825653:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007009692}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"208:14195120:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"208:14195120:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527637631},
			"x":1600,
			"y":5793,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"ibu8iuu4",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**什么是相位滞后？** 想象两列波，一列在真空中，一列在介质中。如果介质中的波相位滞后，就意味着它的波峰到达同一个位置的时间，比真空中的波要晚。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":354,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":354,\"ch\":79}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"176:2012776251:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":180,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":180,"trustedSignature":"176:2012776251:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007009692}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"183:1504186852:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"183:1504186852:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527637631},
			"x":2200,
			"y":5646,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"y46jxtz5",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**相位滞后如何影响速度？** 波的速度是“相位状态”（比如波峰）传播的速度。如果波峰总是“迟到”，从宏观上看，这列波的传播速度就变慢了。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":355,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":355,\"ch\":75}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"172:3484824321:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":180,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":180,"trustedSignature":"172:3484824321:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007009693}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"179:1833201430:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":103,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":103,"trustedSignature":"179:1833201430:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527637631},
			"x":2200,
			"y":5813,
			"width":400,
			"height":103
		},
		{
			"id":"hft5xn63",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**结论：** 相位滞后 $\\implies$ 表观相速度 $v < c \\implies$ 折射率 $n = c/v > 1$。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":356,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":356,\"ch\":71}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"168:776191081:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":109,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":109,"trustedSignature":"168:776191081:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018022}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"175:594326630:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"175:594326630:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527637631},
			"x":2200,
			"y":5956,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"71bzsqzg",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">色散 ( Dispersion) 现象，即折射率随频率（或波长）变化的现象</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":361,\"ch\":49},\"to\":{\"line\":361,\"ch\":86}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"185:3624143198:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":109,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":109,"trustedSignature":"185:3624143198:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018022}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"192:20022185:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"192:20022185:400","trustedTimestamp":1772543770446},
			"x":1600,
			"y":6099,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"p3slv0tj",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"随着频率 $\\omega$ <mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">的增加（从红光到蓝光），相位滞后变大，导致折射率 $n$ 也随之增加</mark>。<mark style=\"background: #76AD62A6;\">这就是为什么棱镜可以把白光分解成彩虹——不同颜色的光在玻璃中有不同的折射率和折射角</mark>。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":361,\"ch\":144},\"to\":{\"line\":361,\"ch\":330}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"285:1424844016:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":216,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":216,"trustedSignature":"285:1424844016:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018022}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"292:575923639:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"292:575923639:400","trustedTimestamp":1772527637631},
			"x":2200,
			"y":6075,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"rk3yglyf",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**Ewald-Oseen 消光定理**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":363,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":363,\"ch\":20}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"123:2382070143:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"123:2382070143:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018022}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"130:1988134924:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"130:1988134924:200","trustedTimestamp":1772543770446},
			"x":1600,
			"y":6278,
			"width":200,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"7fxvdbzl",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"介质中所有分子散射的次级波，可以分解成两部分。一部分恰好在介质内部与原初入射波完全抵消（“消光”）。另一部分则构成了一个新的波，这个波就是我们实际观测到的透射波，它以速度 $v=c/n$ 在介质中传播。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":364,\"ch\":89},\"to\":{\"line\":364,\"ch\":197}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"206:1850365332:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":251,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":251,"trustedSignature":"206:1850365332:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018022}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"213:2709331115:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":151,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":151,"trustedSignature":"213:2709331115:400","trustedTimestamp":1772543770446},
			"x":2200,
			"y":6242,
			"width":400,
			"height":151
		},
		{
			"id":"mqcup3y7",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 4.2.4 超越瑞利散射：米氏散射与几何散射\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":368,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":368,\"ch\":26}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"129:3265136721:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":88,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":88,"trustedSignature":"129:3265136721:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018022}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"136:3068403206:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":97,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":97,"trustedSignature":"136:3068403206:400","trustedTimestamp":1772543770446},
			"x":1000,
			"y":6819,
			"width":400,
			"height":97
		},
		{
			"id":"w0g50u3e",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">米氏散射 ( Mie-Scattering):</mark>** \n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":370,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":370,\"ch\":73}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"175:1929441283:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"175:1929441283:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018022}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"182:2572405417:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"182:2572405417:400","trustedTimestamp":1772543770446},
			"x":1600,
			"y":6615,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"b4uscizu",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"描述的是<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">尺寸与波长相当的球形粒子的散射</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":370,\"ch\":102},\"to\":{\"line\":370,\"ch\":158}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"169:3869654261:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":109,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":109,"trustedSignature":"169:3869654261:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018025}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"176:3150578034:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"176:3150578034:400","trustedTimestamp":1772543770449},
			"x":2200,
			"y":6433,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"glc1ro5o",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">米氏散射对波长的依赖性比瑞利散射弱得多。当粒子尺寸超过波长时，散射几乎与波长无关</mark>。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":371,\"ch\":51},\"to\":{\"line\":371,\"ch\":99}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"189:3452265949:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"189:3452265949:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018025}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"196:2951278919:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"196:2951278919:400","trustedTimestamp":1772543770449},
			"x":2200,
			"y":6528,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"sclevzxi",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"与瑞利散射在前后方向上对称不同，<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">米氏散射的能量更多地集中在前向</mark>。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":372,\"ch\":15},\"to\":{\"line\":372,\"ch\":91}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"180:3711851561:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":109,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":109,"trustedSignature":"180:3711851561:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018025}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"187:991045592:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"187:991045592:400","trustedTimestamp":1772543770449},
			"x":2200,
			"y":6647,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"rf7vzi96",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**例子：** <mark style=\"background: #76AD62A6;\">云和雾由大小与可见光波长相当的小水滴组成。它们对所有颜色的光散射能力都差不多，因此云和雾看起来是白色的。牛奶中的脂肪和蛋白质微粒也是如此。一些白色塑料袋为了不透明，加入了直径约200 nm的二氧化钛微球，它们通过米氏散射发出蓝白色的光</mark>。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":373,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":373,\"ch\":176}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"274:2222235501:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":287,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":287,"trustedSignature":"274:2222235501:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018025}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"281:4098646448:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":175,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":175,"trustedSignature":"281:4098646448:400","trustedTimestamp":1772543770449},
			"x":2200,
			"y":6766,
			"width":400,
			"height":175
		},
		{
			"id":"4uokcymk",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**几何散射 ( Geometrical-Scattering):** \n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":375,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":375,\"ch\":37}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"139:532771849:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"139:532771849:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018025}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"146:1005056819:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"146:1005056819:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":1600,
			"y":7065,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"vsfqoy47",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">当粒子尺寸远大于光的波长时（例如大于10倍波长），光的传播可以用几何光学（光线追迹、反射、折射）来描述</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":375,\"ch\":75},\"to\":{\"line\":375,\"ch\":126}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"200:4142514276:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"200:4142514276:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018026}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"207:1876062818:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":103,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":103,"trustedSignature":"207:1876062818:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":2200,
			"y":6981,
			"width":400,
			"height":103
		},
		{
			"id":"0mlnk0h9",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"<mark style=\"background: #76AD62A6;\">雨滴形成的彩虹就是几何光学的典型例子</mark>。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":375,\"ch\":171},\"to\":{\"line\":375,\"ch\":197}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"169:4203904105:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":109,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":109,"trustedSignature":"169:4203904105:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007018026}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"176:3589776577:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"176:3589776577:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":2200,
			"y":7124,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"ne7oqaoz",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 关键结论与知识点总结\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":379,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":379,\"ch\":14}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"117:4068166444:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":70,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":70,"trustedSignature":"117:4068166444:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024556}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"124:984785129:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":63,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":63,"trustedSignature":"124:984785129:200","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":1000,
			"y":7751,
			"width":200,
			"height":63
		},
		{
			"id":"z90x6m74",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**<mark style=\"background: #FF5582A6;\">散射的本质：</mark>** <mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">散射是光与物质相互作用，导致光向不同方向传播的过程</mark>。在<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">弹性散射中，散射光的频率与入射光相同</mark>。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":380,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":380,\"ch\":193}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"293:1137394638:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"293:1137394638:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024560}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"300:1696382281:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":103,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":103,"trustedSignature":"300:1696382281:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":1600,
			"y":7219,
			"width":400,
			"height":103
		},
		{
			"id":"0swji7g0",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**<mark style=\"background: #FF5582A6;\">瑞利散射：</mark>** <mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">适用于尺寸远小于光波长的粒子（如空气分子）的散射。其核心特征是散射强度与波长的四次方成反比</mark> ($I \\propto 1/\\lambda^4$)。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":381,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":381,\"ch\":174}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"274:4178610184:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":180,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":180,"trustedSignature":"274:4178610184:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024560}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"281:2723798517:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":104,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":104,"trustedSignature":"281:2723798517:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":1600,
			"y":7362,
			"width":400,
			"height":104
		},
		{
			"id":"tcsel2hf",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**天空的颜色：** 瑞利散射解释了天空为何是蓝色的（短波长的蓝光被更强地散射到各个方向），以及日落为何是红色的（长途跋涉后，直射光中只剩下散射较弱的红光和黄光）。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":382,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":382,\"ch\":86}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"185:4229134799:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":216,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":216,"trustedSignature":"185:4229134799:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024560}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"192:3943570692:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"192:3943570692:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":1600,
			"y":7506,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"spoqwtof",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**干涉是关键：**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":383,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":383,\"ch\":14}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"113:3329847498:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"113:3329847498:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024560}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"120:2091821651:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"120:2091821651:200","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":1600,
			"y":7763,
			"width":200,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"60nszlw0",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"在**稀薄介质**中，散射体位置随机，侧向散射的子波相位随机，无系统性干涉，因此可以观测到侧向散射。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":384,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":384,\"ch\":56}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"153:1215744012:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"153:1215744012:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024560}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"160:1660158737:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":103,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":103,"trustedSignature":"160:1660158737:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":2200,
			"y":7673,
			"width":400,
			"height":103
		},
		{
			"id":"31yw8lde",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"在**致密均匀介质**中，散射体位置规则，侧向散射的子波会因相消干涉而极大减弱，导致介质透明。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":385,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":385,\"ch\":53}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"150:608808125:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"150:608808125:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024560}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"157:292080282:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"157:292080282:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":2200,
			"y":7816,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"0qap6qw8",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**前向传播：** 无论介质稀疏或致密，所有散射子波在前向总是相长干涉，使光束得以继续传播。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":386,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":386,\"ch\":50}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"149:1555879026:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"149:1555879026:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024560}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"156:806161499:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"156:806161499:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":1600,
			"y":7935,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"y3xr9ws1",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**<mark style=\"background: #FF5582A6;\">折射率的起源：</mark>** \n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":387,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":387,\"ch\":59}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"159:3831663526:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"159:3831663526:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024560}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"166:4241405935:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"166:4241405935:200","trustedTimestamp":1772529253064},
			"x":1600,
			"y":8090,
			"width":200,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"k76nv1ef",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"折射率 $n>1$ <mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">（光速变慢）的物理本质是，介质中散射再发射的次级波与原初波叠加时产生了**相位滞后**。这使得总的透射波的相位传播速度变慢，而并非单个光子的飞行速度变慢</mark>。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":387,\"ch\":60},\"to\":{\"line\":387,\"ch\":191}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"236:2209755153:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":216,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":216,"trustedSignature":"236:2209755153:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024563}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"243:2943916332:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"243:2943916332:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253065},
			"x":2200,
			"y":8054,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"k0xtutqr",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**散射的分类：**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":388,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":388,\"ch\":14}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"113:2575012975:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"113:2575012975:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024563}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"120:3918558798:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"120:3918558798:200","trustedTimestamp":1772529253065},
			"x":1600,
			"y":8316,
			"width":200,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"vx01vnl0",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**瑞利散射：** 粒子尺寸 $\\ll \\lambda$（蓝天）。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":389,\"ch\":8},\"to\":{\"line\":389,\"ch\":41}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"136:363838777:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"136:363838777:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024563}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"143:2992984064:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"143:2992984064:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253065},
			"x":2200,
			"y":8221,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"wg53eom9",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**米氏散射：** 粒子尺寸 $\\approx \\lambda$（白云、白雾）。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":390,\"ch\":8},\"to\":{\"line\":390,\"ch\":48}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"143:370167049:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"143:370167049:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024563}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"150:2276848414:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"150:2276848414:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253065},
			"x":2200,
			"y":8316,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"aihuhia6",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**几何散射：** 粒子尺寸 $\\gg \\lambda$（用几何光学处理）。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":391,\"ch\":8},\"to\":{\"line\":391,\"ch\":46}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"141:851453798:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":109,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":109,"trustedSignature":"141:851453798:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024563}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"148:605207837:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"148:605207837:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253065},
			"x":2200,
			"y":8411,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"7vkxq8qk",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"<mark style=\"background: #86BDCEA6;\">在瑞利散射中，散射体的精确形状通常无关紧要。散射的强度与散射体直径与入射辐射波长的比值有关</mark>\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":288,\"ch\":84},\"to\":{\"line\":288,\"ch\":129}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"194:3628079090:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"194:3628079090:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007000805}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"201:3038854074:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":103,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":103,"trustedSignature":"201:3038854074:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529246850},
			"x":1600,
			"y":4112,
			"width":400,
			"height":103
		},
		{
			"id":"mif9lklc",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## 4.3 反射 (Reflection)\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":673,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":673,\"ch\":22}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"125:3744035346:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":66,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":66,"trustedSignature":"125:3744035346:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809651}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"132:1323551709:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":123,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":101,"trustedSignature":"125:3744035346:200","trustedTimestamp":1772521877908},
			"x":400,
			"y":10755.158333333333,
			"width":200,
			"height":123
		},
		{
			"id":"ilf0d8wa",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 4.3.1 什么是反射？一个直观的开始\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":676,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":676,\"ch\":24}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"127:3341704058:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":62,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":62,"trustedSignature":"127:3341704058:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007031459}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"134:78532473:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":60,"trustedSignature":"127:3341704058:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521861665},
			"x":1000,
			"y":9141.666666666666,
			"width":400,
			"height":74
		},
		{
			"id":"b927uzku",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"当一束光照射到玻璃等透明材料表面时\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":690,\"ch\":21},\"to\":{\"line\":690,\"ch\":38}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"121:2633242979:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"121:2633242979:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007031462}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"128:4000613098:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":60,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"121:2633242979:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521861665},
			"x":1600,
			"y":9148.666666666666,
			"width":400,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"wqlxkxve",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**悬殊的尺度**：光的波长（$\\lambda$）约为 $500 \\mathrm{~nm}$，而物质中原子的间距仅约 $0.2 \\mathrm{~nm}$。对于光波而言，原子就像一个极其密集的阵列。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":691,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":691,\"ch\":101}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"203:1348098084:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"203:1348098084:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007024563}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"210:3291881573:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":103,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":103,"trustedSignature":"210:3291881573:400","trustedTimestamp":1772529253065},
			"x":2200,
			"y":8506,
			"width":400,
			"height":103
		},
		{
			"id":"7htdursb",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**散射是基础**：当光波（电磁波）扫过原子时，其电场会驱动原子中的电子以相同的频率振荡。根据电磁理论，加速运动的电荷会向外辐射电磁波。这些振荡的电子就像无数个微型天线，向四面八方发射次级波（Wavelets）。这个过程被称为 **散射 ( Scattering )**。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":693,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":693,\"ch\":138}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"240:21622036:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":287,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":287,"trustedSignature":"240:21622036:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007031462}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"247:3442089021:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":156,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":175,"trustedSignature":"240:21622036:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521440310},
			"x":2200,
			"y":8649,
			"width":400,
			"height":175
		},
		{
			"id":"l7mau4eo",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**均匀介质内的“和谐”**：在玻璃内部，远离界面的地方，任何一个原子发出的散射波，在后向和侧向都会被其他原子发出的波精准地抵消掉（相消干涉）。只有在前向，所有散射波会与主光波同相叠加，形成我们看到的透射光束。这就是为什么在均匀介质中，光看起来是直线传播的。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":695,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":695,\"ch\":131}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"233:5878145:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":287,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":287,"trustedSignature":"233:5878145:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007031462}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"240:3215356738:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":156,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":175,"trustedSignature":"233:5878145:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521440310},
			"x":2200,
			"y":8864,
			"width":400,
			"height":156
		},
		{
			"id":"nnbzbbv2",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**界面处的“不和谐”**：反射的秘密在于 **不连续性 ( Discontinuity )**。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":697,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":697,\"ch\":51}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"152:42945959:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":109,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":109,"trustedSignature":"152:42945959:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007031462}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"159:1679728548:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":84,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"152:42945959:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521861665},
			"x":2200,
			"y":9234,
			"width":400,
			"height":84
		},
		{
			"id":"5qwzawhl",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"当光从空气进入玻璃时，介质的性质（如 折射率）发生了突变（在界面处，原子排列突然中断）。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":698,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":698,\"ch\":50}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"147:4144241216:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"147:4144241216:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007039062}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"154:3344456209:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":76,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"147:4144241216:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521861665},
			"x":2800,
			"y":9060,
			"width":400,
			"height":76
		},
		{
			"id":"7by62x51",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"原本应该与后向散射波相互抵消的那部分波，现在缺失了（因为界面另一边没有原子了，或者原子密度变了）。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":699,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":699,\"ch\":55}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"152:2700097582:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"152:2700097582:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007039063}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"159:3313305293:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":76,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":104,"trustedSignature":"152:2700097582:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521861665},
			"x":2800,
			"y":9176,
			"width":400,
			"height":76
		},
		{
			"id":"1uqjj8gt",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"对于界面处的原子，它们在空气一侧没有“伙伴”来产生可以抵消其后向散射的波。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":700,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":700,\"ch\":43}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"140:3356299229:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":109,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":109,"trustedSignature":"140:3356299229:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007039063}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"147:3594631324:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":76,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"140:3356299229:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521861665},
			"x":2800,
			"y":9292,
			"width":400,
			"height":76
		},
		{
			"id":"wyk4wsa8",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"这些“未配对”的原子发出的后向散射波无法被抵消，它们会相干地叠加起来，在宏观上形成了一束方向确定的 **反射 ( Reflection )** 光。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":701,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":701,\"ch\":80}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"177:512847291:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":180,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":180,"trustedSignature":"177:512847291:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007039063}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"184:3116815568:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":108,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":104,"trustedSignature":"177:512847291:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521867066},
			"x":2800,
			"y":9408,
			"width":400,
			"height":108
		},
		{
			"id":"58yswzq4",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"“不连续性”是关键\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":704,\"ch\":5},\"to\":{\"line\":704,\"ch\":14}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"112:1372608318:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"112:1372608318:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007031462}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"119:17160641:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":60,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"112:1372608318:200","trustedTimestamp":1772521867066},
			"x":2200,
			"y":9622,
			"width":200,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"1kntjoot",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"如果介质性质的变化是渐变的（变化距离 $\\ge \\lambda$），反射会极弱\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":704,\"ch\":15},\"to\":{\"line\":704,\"ch\":54}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"143:3427762087:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":109,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":109,"trustedSignature":"143:3427762087:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007039063}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"150:613267324:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":76,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":80,"trustedSignature":"143:3427762087:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521867066},
			"x":2800,
			"y":9556,
			"width":400,
			"height":76
		},
		{
			"id":"fa8zifm3",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"只有当变化发生在极短距离内（$\\le \\lambda/4$），这种突变才会导致我们通常所见的明显反射。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":704,\"ch\":55},\"to\":{\"line\":704,\"ch\":106}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"156:3282107629:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"156:3282107629:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007039063}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"163:1558894076:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":76,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":80,"trustedSignature":"156:3282107629:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521867066},
			"x":2800,
			"y":9672,
			"width":400,
			"height":76
		},
		{
			"id":"rgk2nsv2",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"“不连续性”有一个量化标准\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":706,\"ch\":5},\"to\":{\"line\":706,\"ch\":18}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"116:1724707251:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":74,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":74,"trustedSignature":"116:1724707251:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007031462}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"123:1032207540:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":60,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"116:1724707251:200","trustedTimestamp":1772521867066},
			"x":2200,
			"y":9878,
			"width":200,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"kh0ff86a",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"如果介质性质（如 **介电常数 ( Dielectric-Constant )** 或 **折射率 ( Refractive-Index )** ）的变化是渐变的（变化距离 $\\ge \\lambda$），反射会极弱，界面仿佛不存在\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":706,\"ch\":19},\"to\":{\"line\":706,\"ch\":134}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"220:4113534682:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":180,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":180,"trustedSignature":"220:4113534682:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007039063}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"227:2888174957:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":108,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"220:4113534682:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521867066},
			"x":2800,
			"y":9788,
			"width":400,
			"height":108
		},
		{
			"id":"bmz2jc5g",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"只有当变化发生在极短距离内（$\\le \\lambda/4$），这种突变才会导致强烈的反射\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":706,\"ch\":135},\"to\":{\"line\":706,\"ch\":179}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"150:511739430:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":109,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":109,"trustedSignature":"150:511739430:400","trustedTimestamp":1772007039063}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"157:1878566883:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":76,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":80,"trustedSignature":"150:511739430:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521867066},
			"x":2800,
			"y":9936,
			"width":400,
			"height":76
		},
		{
			"id":"tcswyylw",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 4.3.2 反射的宏观规律：反射定律\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":710,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":710,\"ch\":23}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"126:2160261293:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":61,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":61,"trustedSignature":"126:2160261293:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809651}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"133:895142788:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":60,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":60,"trustedSignature":"133:895142788:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":1000,
			"y":10333,
			"width":400,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"yf7fgl79",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"##### 4.3.2.1 描述光的工具：光线与波前\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":713,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":713,\"ch\":26}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"129:985062586:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":56,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":56,"trustedSignature":"129:985062586:400","trustedTimestamp":1772015105636}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"136:3732107901:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":59,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":59,"trustedSignature":"136:3732107901:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":1600,
			"y":10187.5,
			"width":400,
			"height":59
		},
		{
			"id":"6ancrqkn",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**波前 (Wavefront)**：想象一下向平静的湖面扔一块石头，会产生一圈圈向外扩散的水波。在任意时刻，水波的波峰（或波谷）连接成的线就是一个圆。在三维空间中，这个概念就是 #波前 ( #Wavefront )。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":714,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":714,\"ch\":111}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"213:648706675:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":182,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":182,"trustedSignature":"213:648706675:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809651}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"220:1188679380:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":151,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":151,"trustedSignature":"220:1188679380:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540723118},
			"x":2200,
			"y":10052,
			"width":400,
			"height":151
		},
		{
			"id":"oizhq4f8",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**光线 (Ray)**：虽然光本质上是波，但总画出波前会很繁琐。为了方便地表示光的传播路径和方向，我们引入了 光线 (Ray ) 的概念。**光线是垂直于波前的、代表光能传播方向的假想直线**。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":716,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":716,\"ch\":100}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"202:1518316825:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":182,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":182,"trustedSignature":"202:1518316825:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809652}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"209:3548961966:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"209:3548961966:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":2200,
			"y":10243,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"rsyebogi",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"##### 4.3.2.2 反射定律的内容\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":720,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":720,\"ch\":21}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"124:1901426773:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":56,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":56,"trustedSignature":"124:1901426773:400","trustedTimestamp":1772015105636}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"131:28690776:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":89,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":89,"trustedSignature":"131:28690776:200","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":1600,
			"y":10464.5,
			"width":200,
			"height":89
		},
		{
			"id":"npcy5xp2",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**第一部分：反射角等于入射角。**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":733,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":733,\"ch\":20}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"121:2154239203:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":56,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":56,"trustedSignature":"121:2154239203:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809653}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"128:3880841772:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"128:3880841772:200","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":2200,
			"y":10410,
			"width":200,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"eo6q4czx",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**第二部分：入射光线、反射光线和法线，这三条线位于同一个平面内。**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":741,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":741,\"ch\":37}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"138:2796884656:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":80,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":80,"trustedSignature":"138:2796884656:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809653}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"145:210828043:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"145:210828043:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":2200,
			"y":10529,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"gz35bog1",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 4.3.3 反射的类型：镜面反射与漫反射\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":744,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":744,\"ch\":25}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"128:2076502077:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":92,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":92,"trustedSignature":"128:2076502077:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809653}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"135:3881791352:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":91,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":91,"trustedSignature":"135:3881791352:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":1000,
			"y":10803.5,
			"width":400,
			"height":91
		},
		{
			"id":"44nbhh1i",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**镜面反射 ( Specular-Reflection )**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":748,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":748,\"ch\":34}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"135:4033925066:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":56,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":56,"trustedSignature":"135:4033925066:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809653}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"142:791555979:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"142:791555979:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":1600,
			"y":10696,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"f8pt2oo9",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**漫反射 ( Diffuse-Reflection )**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":751,\"ch\":2},\"to\":{\"line\":751,\"ch\":32}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"133:3328893494:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":56,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":56,"trustedSignature":"133:3328893494:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809654}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"140:2238537307:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":55,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":55,"trustedSignature":"140:2238537307:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":1600,
			"y":10947,
			"width":400,
			"height":55
		},
		{
			"id":"1i752b7a",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"当反射表面非常光滑（其表面的起伏远小于光的波长，光的波长大约是 500 纳米）时，一束平行的入射光线，其反射光线也会是平行的。所有的光都以同样的方式被“整齐地”反射出去。这种反射能够形成像，镜子、平静的水面发生的就属于镜面反射。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":749,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":749,\"ch\":118}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"218:982269114:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":217,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":217,"trustedSignature":"218:982269114:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809654}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"225:102780887:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":151,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":151,"trustedSignature":"225:102780887:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":2200,
			"y":10648,
			"width":400,
			"height":151
		},
		{
			"id":"iqkgi5mh",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"当反射表面非常粗糙（其表面的起伏可以与光的波长相比，甚至更大）时，情况就不同了。虽然对于每一条极细微的光线，在它所照射到的那个微小局部，仍然遵循着“反射角等于入射角”的规律，但是由于表面凹凸不平，每个点的法线方向都各不相同。因此，一束平行的入射光线，其反射光线会射向四面八方。\n    我们能从各个角度看到不发光的物体（如书本、墙壁、衣服），正是因为它们表面发生了漫反射，将光散射到了我们眼睛所在的位置。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":752,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":752,\"ch\":142}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"305:1828904133:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":430,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":430,"trustedSignature":"305:1828904133:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809654}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"313:499616347:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":271,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":271,"trustedSignature":"313:499616347:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":2200,
			"y":10839,
			"width":400,
			"height":271
		},
		{
			"id":"6h1l89np",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 4.3.4 反射的物理本质：原子散射理论\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":764,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":764,\"ch\":25}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"128:3153256050:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":92,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":92,"trustedSignature":"128:3153256050:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809655}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"135:1102749475:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":91,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":91,"trustedSignature":"135:1102749475:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":1000,
			"y":11432.125,
			"width":400,
			"height":91
		},
		{
			"id":"etr5yr8k",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"让我们深入到微观世界，探究反射现象的根本原因。为什么光一碰到介质界面就会被反射回来？\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":765,\"ch\":3},\"to\":{\"line\":765,\"ch\":45}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"145:182352211:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":145,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":145,"trustedSignature":"145:182352211:400","trustedTimestamp":1772015829389}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"152:1804113412:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":79,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":79,"trustedSignature":"152:1804113412:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":1600,
			"y":11150,
			"width":400,
			"height":79
		},
		{
			"id":"03gsfwdm",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"1.  **光的电磁本性与原子相互作用**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":766,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":766,\"ch\":21}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"124:2725809219:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":46,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":46,"trustedSignature":"124:2725809219:400","trustedTimestamp":1772015829389}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"131:59712042:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":41,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":41,"trustedSignature":"131:59712042:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":1600,
			"y":11312,
			"width":400,
			"height":41
		},
		{
			"id":"bn3eqxa7",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"2.  **振动的电子成为新的光源**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":769,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":769,\"ch\":19}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"122:2044071491:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":46,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":46,"trustedSignature":"122:2044071491:400","trustedTimestamp":1772015829389}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"129:2609224028:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":65,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":65,"trustedSignature":"129:2609224028:200","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":1600,
			"y":11467,
			"width":200,
			"height":65
		},
		{
			"id":"akth3dcv",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"3.  **相干叠加决定最终结果**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":772,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":772,\"ch\":18}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"121:2854739620:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":46,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":46,"trustedSignature":"121:2854739620:400","trustedTimestamp":1772015829389}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"128:2469842489:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":60,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":65,"trustedSignature":"121:2854739620:200","trustedTimestamp":1772521871915},
			"x":1600,
			"y":11859,
			"width":200,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"snknikjc",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"光是电磁波，它携带着振荡的电场和磁场。当光波进入一种介质（如玻璃）时，其电场会作用于介质中的原子，特别是原子核外的电子，迫使它们以与光波相同的频率进行受迫振动。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":767,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":767,\"ch\":84}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"183:3615974396:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":216,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":216,"trustedSignature":"183:3615974396:400","trustedTimestamp":1772015829389}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"190:1850106803:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"190:1850106803:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":2200,
			"y":11269,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"5sjzgyv6",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"根据电磁理论，加速运动的电荷会向外辐射电磁波。因此，这些受迫振动的电子就如同一个个微型的天线，向四面八方辐射出新的电磁波（称为**散射子波**）。这些子波的频率与入射光完全相同。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":770,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":770,\"ch\":93}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"192:4288779769:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":216,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":216,"trustedSignature":"192:4288779769:400","trustedTimestamp":1772015829390}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"199:1248670226:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":127,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"199:1248670226:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540710481},
			"x":2200,
			"y":11436,
			"width":400,
			"height":127
		},
		{
			"id":"mpxtrho4",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"我们最终观测到的光（无论是透射光还是反射光），其实是入射光与所有原子散射的子波**相干叠加**（即考虑相位关系地叠加）的结果。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":773,\"ch\":7},\"to\":{\"line\":773,\"ch\":70}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"166:548263260:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":180,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":180,"trustedSignature":"166:548263260:400","trustedTimestamp":1772015829390}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"173:938828627:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":104,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":104,"trustedSignature":"173:938828627:400","trustedTimestamp":1772540718828},
			"x":2200,
			"y":11837,
			"width":400,
			"height":104
		},
		{
			"id":"ghv809qn",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**在均匀介质内部：** 想象一下在玻璃内部，远离界面的地方。对于任何一个原子，它的散射子波在“后向”（与光传播方向相反）会被其后方原子的散射子波所抵消（严格来说是相消干涉）。而在“前向”，所有子波会与主光波同相叠加，使得光波继续向前传播。这就是为什么在均匀的玻璃块中，我们只看到光束一路向前，而看不到向后或向旁的散射光。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":775,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":775,\"ch\":167}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"265:4166187097:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":199,"manualHeight":false}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"272:520366280:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":180,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":199,"trustedSignature":"265:4166187097:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521871915},
			"x":2800,
			"y":11603,
			"width":400,
			"height":180
		},
		{
			"id":"4w7aejqu",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**在介质界面处：** 界面的情况就不同了。对于界面上以及界面附近浅层（大约半个波长深度）的原子，它们在介质外部（例如空气中）没有“伙伴”原子来产生可以抵消它们后向散射的子波。这些“未配对”的原子层发出的后向散射子波无法被完全抵消，它们会进行相干叠加，最终在宏观上形成了一束方向确定的**反射光**。\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":777,\"ch\":6},\"to\":{\"line\":777,\"ch\":156}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"254:3817969043:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":199,"manualHeight":false}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"261:3337387406:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":156,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":199,"trustedSignature":"254:3817969043:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521871915},
			"x":2800,
			"y":11823,
			"width":400,
			"height":156
		},
		{
			"id":"4479gvg8",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**本质上，每一个被光照到的原子都参与了向后散射，但只有界面附近一个薄层（约半个波长厚度）的原子产生的后向散射波能够有效地、相干地叠加形成我们观测到的反射波。**\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":788,\"ch\":4},\"to\":{\"line\":788,\"ch\":85}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"184:4227997249:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":148,"manualHeight":false}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"191:2739210544:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":108,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":127,"trustedSignature":"184:4227997249:400","trustedTimestamp":1772521869426},
			"x":2800,
			"y":12019,
			"width":400,
			"height":108
		},
		{
			"id":"8zfw17l3",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 4.3.5 从微观理论推导宏观定律\n<!-- fromLink:{\"file\":\"Optics/4-Optics/4-Optics.md\",\"from\":{\"line\":790,\"ch\":0},\"to\":{\"line\":790,\"ch\":22}} -->",
			"data":{
				"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"125:315964988:400","lastWidth":400,"lastAutoHeight":61,"manualHeight":false,"trustedHeight":61,"trustedSignature":"125:315964988:400","trustedTimestamp":1772460809655}
			},
			"heightMeta":{"lastSignature":"132:1099887475:200","lastWidth":200,"lastAutoHeight":96,"manualHeight":false},
			"x":1000,
			"y":12167,
			"width":200,
			"height":96
		}
	],
